ued ones (BLUE for peacock and squid; RED for alligator; PURPLE for peacock). Given short horizon and symmetric initial holdings, they will likely keep offers simple: one color for one color, in small quantities, aiming at clear positive gains without heavily optimizing multi-round sequences.",
